N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 5319.40 - Symbol probability

State Regulations

For game types such as spinning reel games or video
spinning reel games, unless otherwise denoted on the pay glass, the
mathematical probability of a symbol appearing in a position for any game
outcome shall be constant. Notes
